  {
    "hotel_id": "6908105",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/jo-joe-paris-gentilly_2/hotel/paris-fr.html",
    "name": "JO&JOE Paris Gentilly",
    "detail": "From what I understood the hostel isn't located in Paris city, however in Paris area, so be careful with what kind of metro tickets you buy. However, generally no problem with that, as there's a metro station a couple of meters away and you can easily get wherever in Paris you need. The hostel in itself is incredible, all in neon lights, there's a roof terrace with a bar, as well as a bar downstairs for your morning coffee, which you can enjoy in a beautiful patio chill area. The staff is very nice and always very helpful. Had the best stay. I had the cabin , which gives you your own personal space,and the price for that is amazingly good; there's enough toilets/showers for everyone, never had to wait. Basically, when I visit Paris again, I'm definitely staying here. Merci Jo&Joe, c'etait une experience incroyable :) ",
